Hunting a Merciless Killer | Garroter | Full Crime Movie

Detroit hangs in the balance, gripped by a chilling wave of brutal murders that has sparked outrage among its citizens. Fear grips the streets as the community clamors for justice. Amid the chaos, one relentless detective has made it his mission to track down the elusive killer terrorizing the city. As the body count rises, the stakes have never been higher in this perilous game of cat and mouse.

2016. Stars: Natalie Peri, Carrie Bradstreet, Connie Kincer
